C.H. Beazer (Holdings) pic v. The Commissioners 1987 VAT TR 164.</mixed-citation>
            </p>
         </fn>
         <fn id="d57e187a1310">
            <label>6</label>
            <p>
               <mixed-citation id="d57e194" publication-type="other">
See Midland Bank pic v. The Commissioners of Customs &amp; Excise, London VAT Tribunal LON/90/785, and
Kingfisher pic v. The Commissioners of Customs &amp; Excise, Manchester VATTribunal MAN/90/344, MAN/90/527;
